snippet.title: EXCLUSIVE: Johnny Depp VS Amber Heard - Day 4
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp arrives at the Royal Courts of Justice for day 4 of his libel trial and waves to BANG's camera on the way in.  

Yesterday (9/7/20) in court it was alleged Depp headbutted ex-wife Amber Heard- which the 57- year-old Pirates of the Caribbean star insisted was accidental. 

Two of Depp's ex- partners, Vanessa Paradis, with who he shares children Lily-Rose and Jack, and Winona Ryder are expected to give their evidence shortly. The case continues.
 
#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #JohnnyVsAmber
